# Host address (adjust port if needed)
@Host = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{Host}}/health
Accept: text/plain

### Create customer (example for vertical-slice CreateCustomer endpoint)
POST {{Host}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

